               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I met a man who said he would give me 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>. to carry it to King-street—I said I would carry it for 9<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.—he said, "Who are you working for?"—I said, "Mr. Sanders"—he said, "If a police? man stops you say it is your master's, and I will give you 1<hi rend="italic">s</hi>."</p>
